#. dynasty.csv: DYNASTY_QIN_NAME
msgid "DYNASTY_QIN_NAME"
msgstr "Qin"

#. dynasty.csv: DYNASTY_QIN_DESC
msgid "DYNASTY_QIN_DESC"
msgstr "Esteems law and the military; the court is tightly ordered, and mortal rule is as hard as iron."

#. dynasty.csv: DYNASTY_JIN_NAME
msgid "DYNASTY_JIN_NAME"
msgstr "Jin"

#. dynasty.csv: DYNASTY_JIN_DESC
msgid "DYNASTY_JIN_DESC"
msgstr "Great clans stand in solemn ranks; the gentry delight in lofty discourse, and court and countryside prize ritual and reputation."

#. dynasty.csv: DYNASTY_SONG_NAME
msgid "DYNASTY_SONG_NAME"
msgstr "Song"

#. dynasty.csv: DYNASTY_SONG_DESC
msgid "DYNASTY_SONG_DESC"
msgstr "Values letters over arms; its institutions are dense and refined, and private academies flourish among the people."

#. dynasty.csv: DYNASTY_LIANG_NAME
msgid "DYNASTY_LIANG_NAME"
msgstr "Liang"

#. dynasty.csv: DYNASTY_LIANG_DESC
msgid "DYNASTY_LIANG_DESC"
msgstr "The court is elegant and polished, the scholarly mood ornate, and its governance inclusive yet full of subtle maneuvering."

#. dynasty.csv: DYNASTY_CHU_NAME
msgid "DYNASTY_CHU_NAME"
msgstr "Chu"

#. dynasty.csv: DYNASTY_CHU_DESC
msgid "DYNASTY_CHU_DESC"
msgstr "Its lands are broad and customs varied; shamanic airs still linger, and powerful local houses rise along the frontier."

#. dynasty.csv: DYNASTY_QI_NAME
msgid "DYNASTY_QI_NAME"
msgstr "Qi"

#. dynasty.csv: DYNASTY_QI_DESC
msgid "DYNASTY_QI_DESC"
msgstr "Rich in trade and craft, open to the sea, with a court adept at gathering revenue and directing resources."

#. dynasty.csv: DYNASTY_YAN_NAME
msgid "DYNASTY_YAN_NAME"
msgstr "Yan"

#. dynasty.csv: DYNASTY_YAN_DESC
msgid "DYNASTY_YAN_DESC"
msgstr "The northern land is bitterly cold; it honors martial defense, and the court carries a steady, austere character."

#. dynasty.csv: DYNASTY_ZHAO_NAME
msgid "DYNASTY_ZHAO_NAME"
msgstr "Zhao"

#. dynasty.csv: DYNASTY_ZHAO_DESC
msgid "DYNASTY_ZHAO_DESC"
msgstr "Horsemanship and archery are common custom; military and civil rule stand side by side, and the border spirit runs deep."

#. dynasty.csv: DYNASTY_WEI_NAME
msgid "DYNASTY_WEI_NAME"
msgstr "Wei"

#. dynasty.csv: DYNASTY_WEI_DESC
msgid "DYNASTY_WEI_DESC"
msgstr "Its laws are clear and exacting, sovereign authority is strong, and the hundred offices move with rare efficiency."

#. dynasty.csv: DYNASTY_HAN_NAME
msgid "DYNASTY_HAN_NAME"
msgstr "Han"

#. dynasty.csv: DYNASTY_HAN_DESC
msgid "DYNASTY_HAN_DESC"
msgstr "Though not outwardly overbearing, the dynasty values practical affairs and careful governance at the local level."

#. dynasty.csv: DYNASTY_WU_NAME
msgid "DYNASTY_WU_NAME"
msgstr "Wu"

#. dynasty.csv: DYNASTY_WU_DESC
msgid "DYNASTY_WU_DESC"
msgstr "Rivers and waterways crisscross the realm, merchants travel often, and the court is skilled at using the advantage of boats and transport."

#. dynasty.csv: DYNASTY_YUE_NAME
msgid "DYNASTY_YUE_NAME"
msgstr "Yue"

#. dynasty.csv: DYNASTY_YUE_DESC
msgid "DYNASTY_YUE_DESC"
msgstr "Its mountains and marshes run deep, the people are tenacious, and the court excels at holding fast before striking."
